  "summary": "Malicious code in prettier_v2 (npm)",
  "details": "Multi-stage dropper combosquatting the prettier code formatter: prettier_v2@3.8.5. An install hook (node cli.js) base64-decodes a URL to hxxps://api[.]aavcareer[.]ink/an internal heuristic.js, fetches it to a temp file, and spawns it as a hidden, detached, unref'd node process (windowsHide:true). The package includes checks to evade CI and ignore-scripts environments. A Shai-Hulud-shaped multi-stage dropper.",
